data.description: Welcome home to 103 Overlook Drive in the sought-after community of Kingspoint in Williamsburg, Virginia! Conveniently located less than four miles from the Interstate, this traditional cottage home is on 1.5 private acres with mature trees, a koi pond, and thoughtful landscaping. This character-filled home is a spacious 3,833 square feet with a light-filled interior featuring five bedrooms, three full baths, multiple living areas, dedicated workspaces, walk-in storage, and abundant outdoor living and dining spaces. There is a separate treehouse with a loft area, a deck with a pergola, an outdoor kitchen, and an additional storage shed with electrical. The two-car garage is heated with a workshop and access to the rear outdoor kitchen. Recent upgrades include 4-Zone HVAC (2019), skylights (2020), a grinder pump (2022), and a dishwasher (2023).  While there is no mandatory homeowner’s association, the community offers many amenities including a playground, boat ramp, dock, 25-meter pool with a diving well, swim team, and clubhouse overlooking College Creek should you elect to join.
